    <link href="https://blogxd.blog/2023/02/26/HowToUseHexo/"/>
    <id>https://blogxd.blog/2023/02/26/HowToUseHexo/</id>
    <published>2023-02-26T14:36:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-12-10T13:29:30.082Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>Hexo Command</h1><p>三件套</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo-cl">$ hexo cl<a class="header-anchor" href="#hexo-cl">#</a></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>git命令行内执行，清理缓存文件</p><h2 id="hexo-generate">$ hexo generate<a class="header-anchor" href="#hexo-generate">#</a></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成静态文件用于部署</p><h2 id="hexo-deploy">$ hexo deploy<a class="header-anchor" href="#hexo-deploy">#</a></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署网站</p><h2 id="启动本地服务器-hexo-server">启动本地服务器 $ hexo server<a class="header-anchor" href="#启动本地服务器-hexo-server">#</a></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地部署<br>登录 <code>http://localhost:4000/</code> 查看</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1&gt;Hexo Command&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;三件套&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ hexo cl&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br</summary>
      
    
    
    
